    .col-sm-12
      %h4 General
      %ul
        %li
          The entry fee is $50 per pool entry. Payment is due by upon registration.
        %li
          Your participation with late payment is solely the commissioner’s decision.
        %li
          The commissioner has final say with any dispute.
        %li
          Registration will end on or about September 5th.
        %li
          The pool will not be split prior to week 15. By entering the contest, the contestant agrees to play until at least week 15 or until the pool ends.
        %li
          In the event of a website malfunction of any kind, the commissioner has final say regarding that week's picks.
        %li
          Choose one team from the current week's NFL schedule that you think will win. If your team wins, you continue in the pool for another week. If your team loses or ties, you are eliminated from the pool. The pool will continue until there is one remaining entrant or the end of the regular season. However, any time after week 14 all remaining entrants may split the pool if 100% of the remaining entrants agree.
        %li
          In the event that all entrants are eliminated in one week, the pool will be divided amongst those entrants.
        %li
          In the event that there are remaining entrants at the end of the regular season, the pool will end and winners will be paid.
        %li
          You may choose a team more than once during the season. You many choose any team that is playing in the current week.
  .row
