      %h4 DEADLINES - Submitting your weekly pick.
      %ul
        %li
          Thursday games: All Thursday games will be locked
          %span.red 1 hour
          %span before the kickoff of the first Thursday game.
        %li
          Sunday and Monday games: All Sunday and Monday games will be locked
          %span.red 1 hour
          %span before the first kickoff of the first Sunday game (excluding international games).
        %li
          International games: All International games will be locked
          %span.red 1 hour
          %span before the start of the first international game.
        %li
          Any pick not submitted prior to those deadlines is defaulted to the first Monday night (MNF) home team.
        %li
          Picks must be submitted via the website at KOPOOL.org.
          %span.red I have NO access to anyone's login credentials and therefore cannot make picks for you.
          %span If necessary, call Dave at 612.710.2578 or email daveandtree@comcast.net.
        %li
          Once your pick is submitted, you may change it as long as your change occurs before the weekly deadlines as described above.
        %li
          All picks will remain confidential until the picks for the week are posted on the website.
        %li
          I plan to launch a new website next year.  This will give us more functionality and security.  The developer will be paid $1,000 from this year’s pool and $1,000 next year, or $1,000 in the year we launch the new site.
        %li
          100% of the money received (less $50+1% for site hosting and maintenance) will be paid to the winner(s). The commissioner is awarded three free pool entries for the administrative duties associated with the pool.
        %li
          The web developers are awarded three free pool entries for system maintenance and future upgrades of KOPOOL.org.
          